Language
--------

* Language meta / function map:
Define mapping between strings and functions tied with regexes for example

* Simple grammar constructs i.e. pipes
Construct sentences using parts of language meta e.g. using special character | or ;


System & Mechanics
------------------

* Using gRPC to split components. Layers:
  - Spec
  - Logic
  - Integration
  They may live in the same address space in an implementation

* UI: vscode extension tu run specs
